snippet.title: Bugsnax Launch Date + Voice Actor Cast Reveal | PS5, PS4, PC - November 12, 2020
snippet.description:
From the minds behind Octodad: Dadliest Catch comes Bugsnax, a whimsical adventure game coming to PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, and Epic Games Store November 12th, 2020. https://www.bugsnax.com

Pre-Order Bugsnax on Epic Games Store: https://www.epicgames.com/store/en-US/product/bugsnax
